    <!-- Visualization & Content Choices: 1. Package Comparison: Report Info -> Package Prices, Photo quantities, Duration, Prints, Video, Santa presence. Goal -> Compare all key features directly. Viz/Presentation -> Responsive HTML Table. Interaction -> Direct side-by-side reading. Justification -> A table offers the clearest and most direct comparison of multiple attributes across different packages. Method -> HTML/CSS/Tailwind. 2. Package Details: Report Info -> All features for each of the 4 packages, including detailed payment plans and specific inclusions/exclusions. Goal -> Inform comprehensively. Viz/Presentation -> 4 styled cards in a responsive grid using HTML/Tailwind, with Unicode icons for key features and a dedicated payment sub-section. Interaction -> Subtle hover effects on cards. Justification -> Cards are highly scannable and ideal for presenting discrete blocks of information, now enhanced with critical financial details. Method -> HTML/CSS/Tailwind. 3. Payment Methods & Terms: Report Info -> General payment options, delivery, extra photos, duration, cancellations, pet policy, image usage, reservations. Goal -> Provide essential logistical and contractual information. Viz/Presentation -> Structured text sections with clear headings and bullet points. Interaction -> None (informational). Justification -> Clear, concise text is best for legal/procedural information. Method -> HTML/CSS/Tailwind. -->
